    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Meanwhile</strong>, peel the cucumber with a vegetable peeler into ribbons</p>\r\n<p><strong>Tip:</strong> keep the soft seedy centre for step 6!</p>\r\n<p><strong>Combine</strong> the rice vinegar and cucumber ribbons in a bowl with a pinch of salt and set aside to pickle until serving&nbsp;</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
